overview: A crisis of feelings, mutual misunderstandings. The man leaves his partner and drives the car along a forest road skidding. The drivers manage to avoid an accident, but when, after a short walk to calm his nerves, he tries to return to the car, he does not find the way back. He does not know yet that he has entered a dangerous area - into the thicket of his shaky self. Will he find relief and reconciliation thanks to his wandering through this mysterious, disturbing "inner" world of memories, desires, dreams and dreams with your partner and yourself ?
title: Gąszcz
